query_result.query:
select * 
from 
(
with 
concat(toString(sc_name), ' (', toString(sc_id) ,')' ) as office_name_id
select office_name_id as `СЦ`, dt as `Дата`, lm as `ПМ`, smc_sorted as `Отсортировано для СЦ`, sms_sorted as `Отсортировано на СЦ`, -diff as `Дельта`
from (
SELECT 
          sc_id,
          dictGet('dict.office_test_d', 'office_name', sc_id) sc_name,
          dt,
          lm,
          sum(smc_sorted) as smc_sorted,
          sum(sms_sorted) as sms_sorted,
          sum(diff) as diff
from reports.smc_sms_diff
where dt >= today()-29
group by 
sc_id, dt, lm
order by sc_id, dt
)
)
